text: Ringkøbing is a town in Ringkøbing-Skjern municipality in Region Midtjylland on the Jutland peninsula in west Denmark. As of 1 January 2010, 9,850 people live in the town.BEF44: Population 1st January, by urban areas database from Statistics Denmark Archeologists believe that the town was started in the 13th century. ==References== Category:Towns in Denmark
title: Ringkøbing
